    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand more on the Mill stuff? Specifically, how would someone use his \"marketplace of ideas\" concept to argue that even \"harmful\" or \"false\" speech shouldn't be regulated by the state?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
